metadata.name: Glitch in the Forest
metadata.description:
There's a magical forest where time and space works differently... the human world is only connected through a portal in a tree named "Old Grey". Sometimes, a glitch occurs... for example, when someone or something passes through the portal.

Originally painted on canvas with mixed media - This version has a few added digital enhancements i.e. the signature in the bottom right corner.

2950 px x 2330 px at 300 dpi
